The 1972  VVAW week long protest (camping on the Mall, marches, speaking to politicians, commaraderie, etc.)<br>
in Washington D.C. was a great catharsis for me after my experiences in Nam. Although I think about Nam most every day, I forgot about the good experience I had in D.C. (I represented Washington State) until I came across this web site. Drive on Mick.
